# .mailmap - Map multiple identities to a single contributor
# Format: Preferred Name <preferred@email.com> <actual@email.com>

# Map all claude commits to Cahce
Cahce <cahce@example.com> <claude@anthropic.com>
Cahce <cahce@example.com> claude <claude@anthropic.com>
Cahce <cahce@example.com> <noreply@github.com>
Cahce <cahce@example.com> claude <noreply@github.com>

# Map other emails to Cahce
Cahce <cahce@example.com> Cahce <ahihidcko@gmail.com>
